<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="heat-v">heat <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hiːt/    美 /hiːt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi (使) 变热；(使) 变暖；(使) 激动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Heat the milk until it boils.
把牛奶煮开为止。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="heat-up">heat up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>加热 (warm up)；变得激烈：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You can try heating up last night's leftovers.
你可以试着热一下昨晚的剩菜。</p><footer>2009 全国改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The election contest is heating up.
选举竞争正在白热化。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>heater /heater/ n [C]   </p></div>